text: Zwei (German: "two") may refer to: * Zwei (band), a Japanese duo band * ZWEI, a text editor * Zwei!!, an action role-playing video game developed by the Nihon Falcom Corporation * Zwei, a team in Infinite Ryvius anime series * Zwei, a character in Phantom of Inferno anime series * Zwei, a Pembroke Welsh Corgi in the anime series RWBY. * Project Zwai, the codename for the video game The Evil Within
title: Zwei
